{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to the  world of &quot;Delivery Mayhem,&quot; where the streets are your playground and the clock is your only enemy. In this top-down, action-packed driving game, you'll become the ultimate package courier, battling against time and competitors to secure your place as the fastest\u2014or perhaps the most destructive\u2014delivery driver in the city. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Design</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Delivery Mayhem&quot; delivers a thrilling and chaotic couch gaming experience that combines high-speed driving with the challenge of delivering packages on time. Navigate through a vibrant top-down cityscape filled with narrow alleys, bustling intersections, and unexpected obstacles. Show off your skills as you weave through traffic, execute drifts, and perform daredevil stunts to reach your destination in record time. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fast-Paced Delivery Action:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race against the clock to deliver packages across a dynamic city. The faster you are, the better \u2014 but be prepared for the unexpected challenges that mayhem brings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/deliveryDestruction.gif?t=1737126588\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Destructive Power-Ups:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embrace chaos with a variety of power-ups that can either boost your speed or unleash havoc on your rivals. From turbo boosts to explosive surprises, use everything at your disposal to gain the upper hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/powerup2.gif?t=1737126588\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Environments:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore diverse city environments, each with its own set of challenges. From the narrow streets of the downtown district to the suburban sprawl, every area presents a new test of your driving and delivery skills.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/environment.gif?t=1737126588\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer Mayhem:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete against friends in local multiplayer mode, adding an extra layer of excitement to the chaos. Who will emerge as the ultimate delivery daredevil?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/together.gif?t=1737126588\" /><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><br>Single player story mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of a young racer seeking revenge against the one responsible for their downfall. Take on daring missions to uncover the mastermind behind the chaos and the destruction of innocent lives. With upgrades, strategy, and skill, conquer the streets, become the ultimate delivery champion, and bring this mayhem to an end!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/singleplayerMissions.gif?t=1737126588\" /> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Start of the Redemption","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745550/a51e927385cc17f76a80b4bda1e5d195e04415a5.jpg"},{"name":"Survived the chasers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745550/4a7fe5d13d0601ebbd1abf0996314171cc080034.jpg"},{"name":"Smelly Underworld Roads","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/i